     &lt;li&gt;Virtual platform change&lt;/li&gt;
     &lt;li&gt;Audio and other formats&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This meeting will be virtual only.&amp;nbsp; This meeting will screen share and use Word documents, PDFs, and PowerPoint presentations.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you need help or have questions, please contact Erica Van Ess at 971-732-6035 or&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="mailto:food.safety@oha.oregon.gov" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(6, 66, 118);"&gt;food.safety@oha.oregon.gov&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

