&lt;h1&gt;Health Care Workforce Committee to meet Nov. 5 via Zoom&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;A public meeting of the Health Care Workforce Committee&lt;/p&gt;

