&lt;p&gt;For more information, please visit the Workforce Committee&rsquo;s website at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://www.oregon.gov/oha/hpa/hp-hcw/pages/index.aspx" style="text-size-adjust: 100%; color: rgb(6, 66, 118);"&gt;https://www.oregon.gov/oha/hpa/hp-hcw/pages/index.aspx&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

