&lt;p&gt;Residential garbage and recycling collection will occur on its regular schedule both days, however extra bags for Fall Clean-Up will not be collected. Customers are encouraged to place cans at the curb by 6:00 a.m. on their standard collection day.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

